          <div purpose="feature-text">
            <h2>A lot can happen in 24 hours</h2>
            <p>Traditional tools make you wait for scheduled check-ins or dig through stale reports. Fleet gives you live results from any device in seconds. When something fails, Fleet shows you exactly what happened and why.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div purpose="three-column-features">
