            <div purpose="feature-title">
              <img alt="Hundreds of data points" purpose="feature-icon" src="/images/icon-data-point-20x20@2x.png">
              <h5>Hundreds of data points</h5>
            </div>
            <p>Access over 350 categories of system data, from installed software and hardware details to network configuration and running processes.</p>
          </div>
          <div purpose="feature">
            <div purpose="feature-title">
              <img alt="Clear diagnostics" purpose="feature-icon" src="/images/icon-diagnostics-20x20@2x.png">
              <h5>Clear diagnostics</h5>
            </div>
            <p>See exactly which commands ran, which scripts succeeded, and which failed, with full error output. Remediate directly from Fleet without interrupting end users.</p>
          </div>
          <div purpose="feature">
            <div purpose="feature-title">
              <img alt="Find what's blocking compliance" purpose="feature-icon" src="/images/icon-shield-20x20@2x.png">
              <h5>Find what's blocking compliance</h5>
            </div>
            <p>When devices aren't compliant, Fleet shows you why. Identify the actual issue and fix it instead of guessing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
